<p>John and Dave have put together a killer Premium show for all of their loyal subscribers today. Topics covered include sending mail remotely, VPN needs for the average user, how Xgrid works, preference problems and much, much more. As always, there&rsquo;s simply too much to list, so support your favorite geeks and subscribe, listen, and enjoy!</p>
<p>Note: Shownotes are complete!</p>
